title: Ontology for Dummies: an estuary ballad

Or other vices
which Jesus Christ is right

Participate procedurally running in circles
Remember embody

Decay

Symbolically speaking
The reapers reaping

Them damn egregores 
Are Whispering sweetly

We’re all Npc’s
In the belly 
of the beast

Red pill blue pill
Bread pill
Mars hill
Or dmt 
Or whatever you feel

God 1 and number 2
It’s all the same damn thing

So clean your damn room
Repent on zoom
Ontology for dummies
A birds eye view
Cuz if you really knew
Could you really even say

The totally depraved
All totally saved
A total disposition from the bed we all made
or is it thee elect
Or are we just insane 

From John Vervaeke 
To Jonathan paguea 
And Jordan Peterson 
To the Chris petkoo show
Paul VanderKlay’s
And grizwald grim and all the dice that he shakes
This Estuary ditty is a little bitty cringy
Ain’t quite the u shaped or heroes journey
all the npc’s in the flood treading in water  to watch you save the day with a bunch a chitter chotter
 From ortho bros
 To Catholic joes
Or Atheistic jobs
To Protestant folks
To Joe shmos 
And Jewish jacobs
And all and everything all in between

So Love the Lord your God with all your heart and soul 
and with all your mind.’
All your fingers and ur toes 
all your neighbors too as if they were your own
